                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18240218-68-off384 t18240218-68-crimeloc386"></join>. On the 4th of February, I was in the shop - an alarm was given - I went out and overtook the prisoner in Plumber-street. I saw him throw this piece of bombazeen down. before I took him - I picked it up, and produce it - it is my master's, and cost 2 l. 8 s. 6 d. It stood between the glass and the street door.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. A man asked me to carry it for him.</p>
               <p>GUILTY. Aged 17.</p>

